{"name":"_?Planar Investigator","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Rather than focusing their elemental bonds to entirely martial ends, a planar investigator’s senses and wit have sharpened as well as their swordplay, allowing them to be the rational leaders of their companions.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">T</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">rapfinding</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 1st level, a planar investigator gains a bonus to Perception to spot traps equal to their level. Computer and Engineering become class skills.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">P</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">lanar </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">I</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">nspiration</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 5th level, a planar investigator can receive guiding words from their planar guide, who can speak with them but not manifest. The planar investigator gains @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.OzwMoyrdE3fcNZLP]{Expertise (Ex)} and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.0HPp0nK0L1VawPYN]{Skill Expertise (Ex)} as an envoy (treating elementalist level as envoy level). This ability replaces fast summons.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">W</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">hispered </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">W</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">arning</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 2nd level, a planar investigator gains a +1 insight bonus to Perception checks to avoid being surprised. At 4th level and every two levels thereafter, this bonus increases by +1 (to a maximum of +10 at 20th level). This ability replaces enduring summon.</span> <br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":false,"sense-dependent":false,"shadow":false,"sonic":false,"summoning":false,"teleportation":false,"water":false},"modifiers":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"sfrpg","systemVersion":"0.22.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672598874646,"modifiedTime":1673334668461,"lastModifiedBy":"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY"},"_id":"1tSjTUluYOj9xeaE","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY":3}}
