{"name":"_?Elemental Assassin","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Drawing the power of the elemental planes internally, some become finely tuned machines to take down targets quickly and efficiently without the help of any so-called guide.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">P</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">recise </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">S</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">trikes</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 1st level, an elemental assassin gains +1d4 of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.MBNI94tbMoqizPUk]{Trick attack} damage (as an Operative). Your effective Operative level for this feature is half your Elementalist Level plus 1 rounded down. This ability replaces summon assistance.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">E</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">vasion</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 5th level, an elemental assassin becomes skilled in their personal movements, gaining @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.EpLSSSdLcqVQKcSM]{evasion} as an Operative. This ability replaces fast summons.</span></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle2\">T</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">alented</span></h3><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 4th level and every 5 levels thereafter, an elemental assassin gains an @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit} (to a maximum of 4 Exploits at 19th level). The elemental assassin treats their elementalist level as their Operative levels when selecting Operative Exploits. This ability replaces enduring summon.</span> <br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":false,"sense-dependent":false,"shadow":false,"sonic":false,"summoning":false,"teleportation":false,"water":false},"modifiers":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"sfrpg","systemVersion":"0.22.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672597182519,"modifiedTime":1673334668461,"lastModifiedBy":"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY"},"_id":"A99iiQ5goU3gQ2uz","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY":3}}
{"name":"|Rock Shards","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">As a standard action, you can hurl a shard of stone at your enemy as a ranged attack, dealing 1d6 slashing and bludgeoning damage + 1 per two elementalist levels. If you are able to make make multiple attacks, you may take a full attack action as normal with this ability. The range of this ability is medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level) and it does not use range increments. Alternatively, when you are using a bow, crossbow, sling or any other ranged and manually reloaded weapon, you deal 1 extra damage per 3 elementalist levels.</span></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"none","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":100,"units":"ft","additional":"10","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"isActive":null,"ability":"","actionTarget":"kac","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[{"name":"Rock Shards","formula":"1d6+floor(@details.level.value/2)","types":{"acid":false,"cold":false,"electricity":false,"fire":false,"sonic":false,"bludgeoning":true,"piercing":false,"slashing":true,"healing":false},"group":null}]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":"","descriptor":"negate"},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":fals