{"name":"__Planar Guide","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">A planar guide’s abilities, base form, and base statistics are determined by the elementalist’s level and chosen planar pact. Planar guides are outsiders for the purpose of determining which spells affect them.</span></p><p>Treat an Elementalist as a Mechanic of their level and the guide as a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.cA0NuGh484BwlDjX]{Drone} with the following exceptions:</p><ol><li><p>A Planar Guide does not get Mods. They do however share whatever Planar Gifts the Elementalist has.</p></li><li><p>A Planar Guide gets 6+int Skill points per Elementalist level.</p></li><li><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The following skills are class skills for planar guides: Bluff (Cha), Profession (Crafting), Mysticism, Perception (Wis), Sense Motive (Wis), and Stealth (Dex). In addition, at 1st level, the elementalist can choose 4 additional skills to be class skills for his planar guide. Note that planar guides with a fly speed receive Acrobatics as a free class skill, even if they do not gain a fly speed until a later level.</span></p></li><li><p>Your Planar Guide can speak one language it's Master does.</p></li><li><p>Your Planar Guide starts with the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.OrRcG0AuwiWBQE2O]{True AI (Ex)} ability.</p></li><li><p>Your Planar Guide has Darkvision 60.</p></li><li><p>At 2nd level your Guide gains @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.EpLSSSdLcqVQKcSM]{Evasion (Ex) (Operative)}. At 15th it gains @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.2N2OH6u4oZnYL6rs]{Improved Evasion (Ex) (Operative)}.</p></li><li><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">A planar guide’s alignment is the same as the elementalist’s and unless otherwise noted its type is outsider (elemental).</span> <br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"><br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"></p></li></ol>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":false,"sense-dependent":false,"shadow":false,"sonic":false,"summoning":false,"teleportation":false,"water":false},"modifiers":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"sfrpg","systemVersion":"0.22.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672515881383,"modifiedTime":1673334668458,"lastModifiedBy":"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY"},"_id":"QbH8pfjOQzBwFRXU"