{"name":"__Planar Gifts","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Planar gifts are gained from an elementalist’s chosen planar pact, granting extra abilities and their guide. Gifts with limited daily uses are drawn from the same pool, whether the elementalist or guide uses it. An elementalist can prevent a guide from activating a limited gift without effort. Unless otherwise noted, activating the power of a gift is a standard action.</span></p><p>An Elementalist gains a Planar Gift at 1st level, 3rd level, and every 4 levels afterwards.</p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The base saving throw of gifts is 10 + ½ elementalist level + the elementalist’s Wisdom modifier.</span> <br style=\" font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \"></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-