{"name":"#Fiery Trail","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Once per day, you can leave a trail of fire behind you (as the </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.hnnmUzbxZ8Zxawaf]{fire wall} </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">spell, caster level equal to elementalist level) in every square you move through until the end of your turn. Using this ability is a free action but it does nothing without movement.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You may choose which side of the square that the wall emanates heat, but it should face the same side the entire path. At 16th level, the damage at all ranges increases by +4 and you may choose to make the wall opaque, blocking line of sight through it for anyone but yourself. At 18th level, you can have both sides of the wall emit heat.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You must be 11th level to select this planar gift.</span></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":false,"sense-dependent":false,"shadow":false,"sonic":false,"summoning":false,"teleportation":false,"water":false},"modifiers":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"sfrpg","systemVersion":"0.22.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672539378988,"modifiedTime":1673334668477,"lastModifiedBy":"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY"},"_id":"dcgqwB4agCnSQgd9","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"7Idr7n4PmaIACOqY":3}}
{"name":"#Perfect Unity","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Once per day, after an effect that includes you is saved against by multiple allies, you may spend a reaction to instead take the best roll among those of your allies and each of your allies also affected may do the same. You may use this ability a second time 14th level and above.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You must be 7th level to select this gift.</span></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":0,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"death":false,"disease":false,"earth":false,"electricity":false,"emotion":false,"evil":false,"fear":false,"fire":false,"force":false,"good":false,"healing":false,"language-dependent":false,"lawful":false,"light":false,"mind-affecting":false,"pain":false,"poison":false,"polymorph":false,"radiation":false,"scrying":false,"sense-dependent":false,"shadow":false,"sonic":false,"summoning":false,"teleportation":false,"water":false},"modifiers":[],"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.dkauTdyLDTOPGjCc"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"sfrpg","systemVersion":"0.22.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672801254924,"modifiedTime":1673334668484