{"name":"\\Form of Water","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">As a standard action, you collapse your body into pure water, retaining your general shape but otherwise becoming entirely liquid. For a number of rounds equal to your Constitution modifier + your elementalist level you only take half damage from slashing and crushing damage. You can @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.universal-creature-rules.u8AzFGnzGkKnTdwZ]{engulf} (as per the universal special ability; DC 10 + your elementalist level + your Strength modifier).</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">While engulfing you deal no damage to the trapped foe but they are unable to breathe air and you can spend a full-round action that provokes attacks of opportunity to perform a combat maneuver check against your trapped target. Success on the combat maneuver check causes the target to immediately begin drowning as you squeeze the breath from them. When you leave this form any engulfed targets are automatically ejected. You may use this ability once per day.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You must be at least 13th level to select this planar gift.</span></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"Con Mod+Level rounds","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"none","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"none","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day"},"isActive":null,"ability":null,"actionTarget":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"charm":false,"cold":false,"compulsion":false,"creation":false,"curse":false,"darkness":false,"dea