{"name":"#Field of Flames","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"chat":"","gmnotes":"","short":"","value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Channeling the raw power of the elemental Plane of Fire, you can become the center point of a roaring column of flames. Creatures within 30 feet of you is engulfed in fire. You may exclude a number of targets equal to your Charisma modifier (you are automatically excluded.) All targets take 1d6 fire damage per elementalist level.</span> <span class=\"fontstyle2\">Creatures make a Fortitude save or are staggered for 1 round. On a success they are not staggered and only take half damage.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You may use this ability once per day. You may use it an additional time at 10th level. Peacefully, you can open a smaller window to heat the local area. Provided an enclosed space, you can entirely avoid damage from even extreme cold temperatures for yourself and anyone within 30 feet. This use of the ability is unlimited.</span></p>","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"All targets in area excluding yourself and up to 1 ally per cha mod","type":""},"area":{"value":30,"units":"ft","shape":"sphere","effect":"burst"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day"},"isActive":null,"ability":"","actionTarget":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","rollNotes":"","damageNotes":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[{"name":"Field of Flames","formula":"(@details.level.value)d6","types":{"acid":false,"cold":false,"electricity":false,"fire":true,"sonic":false,"bludgeoning":false,"piercing":false,"slashing":false,"healing":false},"group":null}]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"fort","dc":"","descriptor":"half"},"descriptors":{"acid":false,"air":false,"calling":false,"chaotic":false,"cha